attachments.title: Various Artists: Skrillex and Diplo Present Jack Ü
attachments.text: The long-rumored Skrillex/Diplo collaboration succeeds on its own specific terms: It's dumb, loud fun from two architects of the dumbest, loudest fun of the 2000s.
